      "special_instructions": "CRITICAL: Avoid Whig history - don't assume progress was inevitable or that earlier thinkers were just 'wrong.' Understand why earlier views seemed compelling. Look for what was lost in transitions, not just what was gained. The history of science is not a triumphal march but a series of ruptures with both gains and losses."
    },
